    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员认为美联储立场更为鹰派，新兴市场外汇指数下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-currencies-slip-as-fed-signals-hawkish-rates-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美联储对明年利率走势发表强硬言论的影响，新兴市场货币指数在美元普遍走强的情况下延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-currencies-slip-as-fed-signals-hawkish-rates-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 11:28:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储会议纪要：市场综述：股市震荡，交易员紧张不安</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股市正试图反弹，交易员重新调整对美联储走势的预期。日本央行维持借贷成本不变后，日元继续走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 22:59:17 GMT</pubDate>
